strings:
<voice_0x010011A3><se_high>Carrie: Well, there they go.
I guess this is goodbye.
<voice_0x010011A4><se_def>Cash: You know, before we met them, I never imagined things would turn out like this.

<voice_0x010011A5><se_def>Cash: I mean, both of us inheriting Dad's fortune?
Who would have believed that?
<voice_0x010011A6><se_def>Cash: Looking back, I can't believe how stubborn we were acting about being sole heirs.
<voice_0x010011A7><se_def>Cash: It's amazing how easily people can change when they put their minds to it.

<voice_0x010011A9><se_high>Carrie: This talk of becoming ‘sole heir’...
It's freaking me out.

<voice_0x010011AA><se_def>Cash: Don't worry. I'm not suggesting anything.
We're in this together.
I swear. On the mark on my palm!

<voice_0x010011AB><se_high>Carrie: I swear it too, Cash.
On the mark of our family...
<voice_0x010011AC><se_high>Carrie: And on the memory of our father.
<voice_0x010011AD><se_high>Carrie: Now that we're working together, we can make the Golding family more successful than it's ever been. Let the good times roll!
